details.name: Psionic Trap
details.description: Templar Assassin places mystical traps that invisibly monitor enemy movement. When sprung at her command, they exert a slowing influence of 30% in the area. Traps charge up to slow 60% after 4 seconds. Deals bonus damage when fully charged.
details.upgrade_description: Grants new ability: Psionic Projection. Allows you to teleport to any Psionic Trap after a brief channel.
